async function loadProduction(){setProductionDefaultDateRange();resetProductionEntriesCollapse();const p=new URLSearchParams({branch:$('prodBranch').value||'All',start:$('prodStart').value||currentMonthStartISO(),end:$('prodEnd').value||todayISO()});if($('prodEmployee').value)p.set('employee_id',$('prodEmployee').value);const d=await api('/api/production?'+p);state.production=d;renderProduction()}
function renderProductionEntriesTable(entries=[]){const body=$('productionEntriesBody'),scope=$('productionEntriesScope'),toggle=$('toggleProductionEntriesBtn'),colspan=has('production_write')?10:9;if(!body)return;if(!entries.length){body.innerHTML=`<tr><td colspan="${colspan}">No daily entries found.</td></tr>`;if(scope)scope.textContent='';if(toggle)toggle.classList.add('hidden');return}const today=localDateISO(),dates=[...new Set(entries.map(r=>r.date).filter(Boolean))].sort((a,b)=>b.localeCompare(a)),target=dates.includes(today)?today:dates[0],hiddenCount=entries.filter(r=>r.date!==target).length,visible=productionUi.entriesExpanded?entries:entries.filter(r=>r.date===target);body.innerHTML=visible.map(r=>{const day=new Date(r.date+'T00:00:00').toLocaleDateString('en-US',{weekday:'long'});const producedLabel=['Body','Joint/Side'].includes(r.activity)?'<small>Paired in summary</small>':num(r.quantity);return `<tr class="${day==='Friday'?'friday-row':''}"><td>${r.date}</td><td>${day}</td><td>${r.employee}</td><td>${r.branch}</td><td>${r.activity}</td><td>${r.quantity}</td><td class="status-profit">${producedLabel}</td><td>${r.ot_hours}</td><td>${r.entered_by}</td>${has('production_write')?`<td><button class="action-btn" onclick="editProduction(${r.id})">Edit</button><button class="action-btn delete" onclick="deleteProduction(${r.id})">Delete</button></td>`:''}</tr>`}).join('');if(scope){const dateLabel=target===today?"today's entries":`latest entries from ${target}`;scope.textContent=productionUi.entriesExpanded?`Showing all ${entries.length} entries in the selected range.`:`Showing ${visible.length} ${dateLabel}.`}if(toggle){toggle.classList.toggle('hidden',hiddenCount===0);toggle.textContent=productionUi.entriesExpanded?'Show Less':`Show More (${hiddenCount})`}}
function renderProduction(){const {entries,summary}=state.production,dailyReady=state.production.daily_ready||[];const totalQty=summary.reduce((a,x)=>a+num(x.total_quantity),0),produced=summary.reduce((a,x)=>a+num(x.total_pcs_produced),0),readyCompleted=num(state.production.ready_total),ot=summary.reduce((a,x)=>a+num(x.ot_hours),0);$('productionKpis').innerHTML=[['Total Activity Qty',totalQty,'All employee work recorded'],['Total Stage Pcs Produced',produced,`${summary.length} employees with entries`],['Total Ready Completed',readyCompleted,'Final day-end completed dishdashas'],['Overtime Hours',ot.toFixed(1),'Recorded overtime']].map(c=>`<div class="kpi-card"><div class="kpi-label">${c[0]}</div><div class="kpi-value">${c[1]}</div><div class="kpi-note">${c[2]}</div></div>`).join('');
 $('dailyReadyCompletedBody').innerHTML=dailyReady.map(r=>{const day=new Date(r.date+'T00:00:00').toLocaleDateString('en-US',{weekday:'long'});return `<tr class="${day==='Friday'?'friday-row':''}"><td>${r.date}</td><td>${day}</td><td>${r.branch}</td><td class="ready-completed-value">${num(r.total_ready_completed)}</td><td>${r.notes||'—'}</td><td>${r.entered_by}</td>${has('production_write')?`<td><button class="action-btn" onclick="editReadyCompleted(${r.id})">Edit</button><button class="action-btn delete" onclick="deleteReadyCompleted(${r.id})">Delete</button></td>`:''}</tr>`}).join('')||'<tr><td colspan="7">No Total Ready Completed record has been entered for this date range.</td></tr>';
 $('productionSummaryBody').innerHTML=summary.map(r=>`<tr><td><strong>${r.employee}</strong></td><td>${r.branch}</td><td>${num(r.body)}</td><td>${num(r.joint_side)}</td><td class="status-profit">${num(r.full_body_produced)}</td><td>${num(r.daraz)}</td><td>${num(r.vip_design)}</td><td>${num(r.button)}</td><td>${num(r.alteration)}</td><td>${num(r.cutting)}</td><td>${num(r.iron)}</td><td>${num(r.total_quantity)}</td><td class="status-profit">${num(r.total_pcs_produced)}</td><td>${num(r.ot_hours)}</td><td><button class="link-btn" onclick="openHistory(${r.employee_id})">View History</button></td></tr>`).join('')||'<tr><td colspan="15">No production data found.</td></tr>';
 renderProductionEntriesTable(entries);applyUserUI()}
$('prodBranch').onchange=async()=>{const current=$('prodEmployee').value;const list=employeeListForBranch($('prodBranch').value);$('prodEmployee').innerHTML='<option value="">All Employees</option>'+list.map(e=>`<option value="${e.id}">${e.name}</option>`).join('');if([...$('prodEmployee').options].some(o=>o.value===current))$('prodEmployee').value=current;else $('prodEmployee').value='';await loadProduction()};$('prodEmployee').onchange=loadProduction;$('applyProductionFilter').onclick=loadProduction;['prodStart','prodEnd'].forEach(id=>{const el=$(id);if(el)['input','change'].forEach(evt=>el.addEventListener(evt,()=>{productionUi.dateRangeTouched=true;resetProductionEntriesCollapse()}))});$('toggleProductionEntriesBtn').onclick=()=>{productionUi.entriesExpanded=!productionUi.entriesExpanded;renderProduction()};
